         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">353.  ¶  ¶ Datura Stramonium L. ¶  ¶  ¶ Very dangerous to herds &amp; flocks; should be pulled and at once burnt where ever it appears, particularly before ripening seeds. ¶ 356.  ¶  ¶ Teucrium racemosum ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.00.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Jessie Hussey</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">State Library of South Australia, Adelaide, South Australia.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>353. <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Datura Stramonium L.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Very dangerous to herds &amp; flocks; should be pulled and at once burnt where ever it appears, particularly before ripening seeds.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">356. <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Teucrium racemosum R. Br.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">354. <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gahnia Mariscus F.v.M.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Feel honored and delighted with your portrait,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">cite.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> with its touching happiness of expression. Kindly accept my poor lithogram.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your last Algs have gone to Prof. Agardh.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With friendship your</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The malvaceous plant is a Lavatera, one of about 20 species occurring at the mediterranean Sea. I will give the specific name later. Could you send a fruiting specimen?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
